reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I once knew a surfer girl from Italy visiting Hawaii where I lived and she was obsessed with these bracelets. She had them over half her forearm. So I wanted some because she loved them so much. These are just like what she had, soft embroidery floss woven into patterns. They look so friendship bracelet style. You get 5 plus 1 beads bracelet. Soft, smooth, clean edges, nice designs sewn in and not just stamped on. Easy to put on, simply pull a string end to tighten. Can be done one handed by yourself. Easy to keep on all the time, get wet, shower, sleep, comfortable bracelets. Give a couple away as friendship and keep some and wear them til they fall off on their own like the girl from Italy did. I like the style and design and the surfer boho hippie concept. Happy to have these! Exactly as expected. I especially love the little pink flower one against the brown background.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars THESE BRACELETS ARE A GREAT VALUE
reviews.reviewText: THESE BRACELETS ARE A GREAT VALUE! These are nice quality, and such a value at this price! They slide easily and are easy to get off and on. I also like that the elasticated bracelet fits me—I have a 7.5” wrist, and it seems like stretchy bracelets are often just a bit tight, but not this one.LOVELY set and I HIGHLY RECOMMEND!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality and size adjusts easily
reviews.reviewText: They are good looking colors that compliment each other if you wanted to wear more than one together. The adjustment strings pull in and out smoothly and hold well. Have gotten compliments on them already. They are all equally sized in thickness and length. Other sets I've had weren't equal so they didn't look like they went together. The pictures show people wearing them on their wrists but the description says anklet bracelets which is what I think they probably are although they fit ok on my wrists. If you have small wrists they may be a little large to wear around your wrists.
